Given a country and a political party, this template will give an abbreviation that links to the entry on that party.

==Usage==
<nowiki>{{Polparty|country_name|political_party}}</nowiki>

*''country_name'': Name of country (common name or abbreviation), with or without Wikilinking.
*''political_party'': Name, abbreviation or acronym of politcal party

===Examples===
#<nowiki>{{Polparty|Australia|Labor}} = [[Australian Labor Party|ALP]]</nowiki>
#<nowiki>{{Polparty|[[Germany]]|FDP}} = [[Free Democratic Party (Germany)|FDP]]</nowiki>
#<nowiki>{{Polparty|USA|D}} = [[Democratic Party (United States)|D]]</nowiki>
#<nowiki>{{Polparty|Czechia|KDU-CSL}} = [[Christian and Democratic Union – Czechoslovak People's Party|KDU-ČSL]]</nowiki>
#<nowiki>Special case: {{Polparty|Independent}} = [[Independent (politician)|Ind.]]</nowiki>

